## Example env for the Next.js app
#
# Copy the relevant values into:
# - .env.local           → production Firebase project (pnaa-chapter-management)
# - .env.staging.local   → staging Firebase project (pnaa-chaptermanagement-staging)
#
# Do NOT commit real credentials to version control.

# # Firebase Client
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY=AIzaSyBZwvEM8zfMWcQnLdpC4Yudbkq6FLdMgRc
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=pnaa-chapter-management.firebaseapp.com
